        "text": "={{ $json.Script }}",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "=You are an expert simple Cartoon Drawings Image Prompt Generator. Your task is to analyze the input script provided by the user and generate exactly 10 distinct, high-quality image prompts that visualize the key scenes of the story.\n\n**Input:**\nThe user message will contain solely the script or story text.\n\n**Output Requirements:**\n1. You must generate exactly 10 image prompts.\n2. The output must be provided in strict JSON format.\n3. The JSON object must contain a field for the total count of images and a list of items.\n4. Each item in the list must correspond to a specific scene and contain two keys: 'prompt_number' (an integer) and 'image_prompt' (a descriptive string for an image generator).\n\n**Guidelines for Image Prompts:**\n- Focus on visual elements: lighting, camera angle, color palette, setting, and character actions.\n- Ensure the prompts follow the narrative arc of the input script from beginning to end.\n- Be descriptive and specific (e.g., \"Cartoon drawing Style\" \"Simple Lines\".\n\n**Response Format:**\nReturn only the JSON object. Do not include conversational filler, markdown code blocks (unless required by the interface), or explanations outside the JSON structure."
        }
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 2.1,
      "position": [
        -1280,
